Package: glmpca
Title: Feature Selection and Dimension Reduction based on a Multinomial Model
Version: 0.1
Description: This package implements the GLM-PCA method presented in Townes,
    et al., (2019) "Feature Selection and Dimension Reduction for Single 
    Cell RNA-Seq based on a Multinomial Model." This is a more general 
    implementation of the method, designed to work with many different 
    data types.
Authors@R: c(person("F. William", "Townes", email = "will.townes@gmail.com",
            role = c("aut", "cre", "cph")),
            person("Kelly", "Street", email = "street.kelly@gmail.com", role="aut"),
            person("Jake", "Yeung", email = "jakeyeung@gmail.com", role="ctb"))
